---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import '../styles/pages.css';
---

<Base title="About" titleZh="关于" description="How Taste Bank turns visual references into reusable front-end systems." wide>
  <main class="subpage about-page">
    <div class="about-layout">
      <header class="about-intro">
        <p class="eyebrow"><span data-ui-en>About Taste Bank</span><span data-ui-zh>关于 Taste Bank</span></p>
        <h1>
          <span data-ui-en>Visual taste,<br /><em>made usable.</em></span>
          <span class="cn-display" data-ui-zh>视觉品味，<br /><em>转化为系统。</em></span>
        </h1>
      </header>
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="about-lead"><span data-ui-en>Taste Bank turns visual references into front-end directions that coding agents can actually apply.</span><span data-ui-zh>Taste Bank 将视觉参考转译为 coding agent 真正能够执行的前端方向。</span></p>
        <div class="method-list">
          <article>
            <h2><span data-ui-en>Collect</span><span data-ui-zh>收集</span></h2>
            <p><span data-ui-en>Start from a real interface with a distinct point of view, not an abstract mood board or a list of fashionable adjectives.</span><span data-ui-zh>从观点鲜明的真实界面出发，而不是抽象情绪板或流行形容词的堆叠。</span></p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <h2><span data-ui-en>Translate</span><span data-ui-zh>转译</span></h2>
            <p><span data-ui-en>Extract typography, spacing, color, motion, voice, and explicit constraints into a structured style pack.</span><span data-ui-zh>提取字体、间距、色彩、动效、语气和明确约束，整理为结构化风格包。</span></p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <h2><span data-ui-en>Build</span><span data-ui-zh>构建</span></h2>
            <p><span data-ui-en>Give the complete skill, tokens, and templates to a coding agent so the visual intent survives implementation.</span><span data-ui-zh>将完整的 skill、tokens 和 templates 交给 coding agent，让视觉意图完整进入实现。</span></p>
          </article>
        </div>
        <p class="about-signoff"><span data-ui-en>Created and maintained by QuasarG.</span><span data-ui-zh>由 QuasarG 创建并维护。</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
